  "body": "Many users inadvertently try to sync from genesis cause they do not know about checkpoint sync (for example our documentation does not mention it in the quickstart guide). Besides fixing the docs, I think a good UX would be to \r\n\r\n- Add a feature flag `--sync-from-genesis`. \r\n-  When starting a node on an empty db, refuse to sync unless one of `--sync-from-genesis` or  one of the `--checkpoint-sync` flags is set. ",
